description.en:
OKBoomer Token is a project focused on cryptocurrency education and crypto-friendly regulation. There is an education system of videos and tools rolling out accessible to token holders. There is an exclusive NFT line in collaboration with former professional athletes being used as an education tool on what non-fungible tokens are and how to trade them.
OKBoomer is a deflationary frictionless yield generating protocol which applies a 10% tax on buy and sell transactions and has no fees on wallet-to-wallet transfers or donations.
